{"ts": "2026-06-08T23:45:57.699151+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: de583d0940d6ec7a20f3b3a29172729e87173fcf)", "id": "lc_d6c2378b-c09c-4aec-b284-f7d28c6fb81e"}, {"type": "text", "text": "# just a flag\nENV = 'development'\n\n# base api\nVUE_APP_BASE_API = '/dev-api'\n", "id": "lc_3c35ecce-1cae-4c39-b41a-4a108dc4b835"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "7c85b954-74d0-4bda-a85b-c50c0c14f374", "tool_call_id": "call_a2f3d6d42b884e189a1ac28d", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-08T23:45:57.699252+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 0c57de2aad9ee533046b71c08b56943be304d867)", "id": "lc_e3894dbb-2962-46b1-aad7-bc688c38f6d2"}, {"type": "text", "text": "const { run } = require('runjs')\nconst chalk = require('chalk')\nconst config = require('../vue.config.js')\nconst rawArgv = process.argv.slice(2)\nconst args = rawArgv.join(' ')\n\nif (process.env.npm_config_preview || rawArgv.includes('--preview')) {\n  const report = rawArgv.includes('--report')\n\n  run(`vue-cli-service build ${args}`)\n\n  const port = 9526\n  const publicPath = config.publicPath\n\n  var connect = require('connect')\n  var serveStatic = require('serve-static')\n  const app = connect()\n\n  app.use(\n    publicPath,\n    serveStatic('./dist', {\n      index: ['index.html', '/']\n    })\n  )\n\n  app.listen(port, function () {\n    console.log(chalk.green(`> Preview at  http://localhost:${port}${publicPath}`))\n    if (report) {\n      console.log(chalk.green(`> Report at  http://localhost:${port}${publicPath}report.html`))\n    }\n\n  })\n} else {\n  run(`vue-cli-service build ${args}`)\n}\n", "id": "lc_f0963352-cbfa-46e5-921f-432336d129f8"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "dd6913a0-1987-47fe-9b39-2da10a3f7410", "tool_call_id": "call_3eda159d1aac45e0b14e8bcc", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-08T23:46:12.226081+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Based on the repository contents, here's a summary of how to start the admin app locally and how to build/preview it for staging and production:\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 Local Development\n\n### Prerequisites\n1. Clone the repository:\n   ```bash\n   git clone https://github.com/HaitaoWang555/vue3-admin-template.git\n   cd vue3-admin-template\n   ```\n\n2. Install pnpm (package manager):\n   ```bash\n   npm i -g pnpm\n   ```\n\n3. Install dependencies:\n   ```bash\n   pnpm install\n   ```\n\n### Start Development Server\n```bash\npnpm dev\n```\n\n**Result:** Automatically opens http://localhost:9528\n\n**Environment:** Uses `.env.development` with:\n- `VUE_APP_BASE_API = '/dev-api'`\n\n---\n\n## 🔨 Building for Staging and Production\n\n### Build for Staging (Test Environment)\n```bash\npnpm build:stage\n```\n\n**Environment:** Uses `.env.staging` with:\n- `NODE_ENV = production`\n- `VUE_APP_BASE_API = '/stage-api'`\n\n### Build for Production\n```bash\npnpm build:prod\n```\n\n**Environment:** Uses `.env.production` with:\n- `VUE_APP_BASE_API = '/prod-api'`\n\n---\n\n## 👀 Previewing Builds\n\nAfter building, you can preview the output:\n\n### Preview Staging/Production Build\n```bash\npnpm preview\n```\n\nThis will:\n1. Run `vue-cli-service build` with the current mode\n2. Start a static server on **port 9526**\n3. Serve the `./dist` directory at the configured `publicPath`\n\n**Access:** http://localhost:9526\n\n### Preview with Static Resource Analysis\n```bash\npnpm preview -- --report\n```\n\nThis adds a bundle analysis report at http://localhost:9526/report.html\n\n---\n\n## 📋 Quick Reference Table\n\n| Task | Command | Port | Environment File |\n|------|---------|------|------------------|\n| Local development | `pnpm dev` | 9528 | `.env.development` |\n| Build staging | `pnpm build:stage` | - | `.env.staging` |\n| Build production | `pnpm build:prod` | - | `.env.production` |\n| Preview build | `pnpm preview` | 9526 | (uses current mode) |\n| Preview + report | `pnpm preview -- --report` | 9526 | (uses current mode) |\n| Lint code | `pnpm lint` | - | - |\n| Auto-fix lint | `pnpm lint -- --fix` | - | - |\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 Additional Notes\n\n- **Package Manager:** The project uses **pnpm** (not npm or yarn)\n- **Framework:** Vue 3 with Vue CLI Service\n- **UI Library:** Element Plus\n- **CSS Framework:** Tailwind CSS\n- **State Management:** Vuex 4\n- **API Base URLs:**\n  - Development: `/dev-api`\n  - Staging: `/stage-api`\n  - Production: `/prod-api`", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 786, "prompt_tokens": 7451, "total_tokens": 8237, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 109, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 6656, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0010536066, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0003697866, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00068382}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780962358-OrA4Ue9hORpNUR5uXeAR", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea9a0-f1c3-7c43-a03d-1af67e3b0fa5-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 7451, "output_tokens": 786, "total_tokens": 8237, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 6656}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 109}}}}]}}}
